name: Audio Processing Framework (APF)
tagline: C++ library for multichannel audio programming
body:
The Audio Processing Framework (APF) is a collection of C++ code which was written in the context of multichannel audio applications. However, many modules have a more generic scope.

### Links

Development pages: http://github.com/AudioProcessingFramework/apf

Doxygen documentation: http://AudioProcessingFramework.github.com/apf-doc

Blog: http://spatialaudio.net
